Package io.barracks.ota.client.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UpdateCheckApi
    This interface describes the call to the Barracks platform which requests UpdateDetails.
    UpdateDownloadApi
    This interface describes the call to the Barracks platform which downloads a package.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PackageInfo
    This class encapsulates the details about an update package.
    UpdateDetails
    This class encapsulates the details about an update.
    UpdateDetailsRequest
    This class encapsulates parameters to request UpdateDetails to the Barracks service.
    UpdateDetailsRequest.Builder
    A convenient builder to create an UpdateDetailsRequest.
